title: Microsoft Syntex: Accounts Payable In-product site template
description: Licensed Syntex users will be able to apply an accounts payable site template directly from the in-product template gallery.  This template includes automatic data classification and extraction using a prebuilt invoice model, a preconfigured content assembly model and various sample webparts, lists and libraries to inspire you. It also includes learning material about how to use and extend this template to customize it for your own use case!
